metadata.name: Chapter 1: The Birth of Bobo
metadata.description:
A space ship drifts slowly within a cold starry space. A purple glow of energy illuminates the inner ship, falling upon a new born child. A child named Bobo.

The new parents gaze at him. Happy and delighted as their new born son begins to smile. Suddenly, it's as if the void around them begins to shine even brighter. 

The mother telekinetically wraps her son in a green fabric cloth. Laying him upon the bed of the ship. And as the stars begin to shine, a new star is born. 

And so the legend begins. 

Bobo The Epic.
